snippet.textDisplay:
Wow, this Coke Studio rendition of our Kashmiri cultural song is absolutely mesmerizing! The artists have done a brilliant job in capturing the essence and beauty of our heritage. The melody, the vocals, and the traditional instruments blend seamlessly to create a truly enchanting experience. It's heartwarming to see our rich Kashmiri culture being celebrated and shared with the world through such a platform. This rendition is a true testament to the talent and creativity of our musicians. Kudos to Coke Studio for highlighting and preserving our musical heritage in such a captivating way. Proud to be a part of this cultural legacy!"
Thank you coke studio ❤❤❤

snippet.textDisplay: This song... It's a mosaic of feelings on the wedding of a daughter... The kori mol or the father of the bride, this song weaves his worries and hopes and all his desperation into a celebration... The part of the bride really touched my heart... It's such a heart-breakening  part... leaving everything behind and stepping into an unchartered territory just with the hope in Almighty... Every Kashmiri korimol and khanamouj koor has lived this song... every inch of it
